{"tid":822971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔關山竹事]有冇人屋企人管得好嚴","createTime":"2018-09-16T14:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T15:42:58.000Z","uid":208040,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37b715c647ed29b256615f474101dfbd3873b023","tid":822971,"uid":208040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"一年前 就已經因為會阻住DSE迫我同男朋友講分手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />year3先畀拍拖 <br />\n<br />\n當我用70蚊買咗兩件特價衫 <br />\n係床上邊幫部電話插電<br />\n打漏咗一個電話返屋企<br />\n全部咁小嘅事 都可以用 3 4 個鐘嚟話我<br />\n<br />\n一開始我會駁嘴 後尾我放棄 <br />\n<br />\n我點認錯都好 即刻講對唔住 剖析埋自己點錯點唔啱 <br />\n佢地都可以話我即刻道歉係扮曬野 好唔真誠 跟住又搵第二樣野入我 我講咩都冇用 係咁喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最勁個次三日喊咗七次 喊足三日三夜 <br />\n<br />\n有一次係度吵 老豆話我平時講咁多野調解佢同我老母關係係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">挑撥離間</span>  <br />\n又話我一直以嚟堅持嘅興趣係無出息 咩都係半桶水 <br />\n我忍唔住 將個頭係咁撼埋牆  佢淨係會好大聲咁鬧：你對唔住我ar！<br />\n<br />\n琴日我阿媽趁我未起身將我隻倉鼠帶出街玩 返嚟就整唔見咗隻倉鼠 <br />\n佢淨係講佢好傷心 呢個係隻鼠嘅命 要唔見佢都無辦法<br />\n我點都估唔到 佢一句對唔住都冇 就話我對佢仲冇隻倉鼠對佢咁好咁熱情 我一粒聲都冇出過 佢就講咗一個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭先打風啱啱瞓醒 佢地問我啲野 我燥燥地皺咗一下眉 就又係度鬧點可以咁對佢 就好似皺眉係殺咗人咁<br />\n<br />\n主動做家務 又話我做得差唔畀我做 <br />\n<br />\n成日因為啲咁無聊嘅野而吵真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日日返到屋企就係畀人鬧<br />\n<br />\n咩都要迫到人盡先開心<br />\n<br />\n話我對佢地唔好 成日唔同佢地講野 咪又係因為無論我做啲咩講啲咩佢地都會話我 <br />\n<br />\n係屋企平靜嘅日子唔會超過3日<br />\n<br />\n真係好絕望 又冇勇氣離家出走 <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲感同身受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a315678a5de85c600c6dded293e01fd9f05bc876","tid":822971,"uid":141022,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:52:57.000Z","msg":"忍多幾年 到時出黎做野努力搵錢搬出去住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6bf53fee0f2a0ae13d3403d07b0dc90c07e5f9","tid":822971,"uid":201931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"倉鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係呢件事都夠我嬲佢十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f325dc57be813a9fbf9b3e209d1e2cce6c2f7d8e","tid":822971,"uid":208040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b6bf53fee0f2a0ae13d3403d07b0dc90c07e5f9","tid":822971,"uid":201931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"倉鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係呢件事都夠我嬲佢十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"倉鼠係公園度唔見 仲要打風 好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4644a26af79fe7680a58601691cf1a109aac7115","tid":822971,"uid":208040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a315678a5de85c600c6dded293e01fd9f05bc876","tid":822971,"uid":141022,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:52:57.000Z","msg":"忍多幾年 到時出黎做野努力搵錢搬出去住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"我驚到時我會一世唔返娘家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17214fb1ff070158e0ca91fe9dc553d7cf170647","tid":822971,"uid":72690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"做野就搬出去住"},{"pid":"566177f6c12e9e9d4b9fd9d6ede111beca42f35d","tid":822971,"uid":119413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f325dc57be813a9fbf9b3e209d1e2cce6c2f7d8e","tid":822971,"uid":208040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b6bf53fee0f2a0ae13d3403d07b0dc90c07e5f9","tid":822971,"uid":201931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"倉鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係呢件事都夠我嬲佢十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj